# ğŸ–¼ï¸ Easy NFT Market Place
**GitHub Repository**: [github.com/Chujimafa/easy-NFT-Market-Place](https://github.com/Chujimafa/easy-NFT-Market-Place)

A simple, ERC20-based NFT marketplace built using **Hardhat**, **Ethers.js v6**, and **React** frontend. It allows users to list, buy, and delist NFTs securely.

> âš ï¸ `TestPaymentToken` and `TestNft` contracts are **for testing purposes only** and **deployed only on the local Hardhat network**.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- âœ… List NFTs with ERC20 token pricing (e.g. USDC)
- âœ… Buy NFTs using ERC20 tokens
- âœ… Delist NFTs from the marketplace
- âœ… React + Ethers.js v6 frontend
- âœ… Complete unit test suite using Hardhat Network Helpers


